OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fbecoming less frequent into the
OL,7,Fevening, before skies cloud over from
OL,8,Fthe west later in the night, with
OL,9,Fshowery outbreaks of rain reaching the
OL,10,Farea towards dawn. Turning chilly in
OL,11,Frural spots under the clearest skies.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FCloudy with showery
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain during the morning.
OL,15,FSome sunny or bright spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping, however a continued risk
OL,17,Fof showers with hail and thunder,
OL,18,Fbefore these fade towards evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
